snippet.title: Will this BS Conversion Work? - BS Super Mario USA 1 fan translation (Con, pacnsacdave)
snippet.description:
On the bright side, this worked a lot better than BS Zelda did.

I can also do tests for 2, 3 and 4 as well. Though If this one works fine then the others logically should as well.

YouTube is telling me to tell people to join and become a member for reasons, so here's the link for that ~
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOXvfoAZZJhmDZw0boGkSYA/join
